content: अप्रतिष्ठ {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Not stable or firmly fixed, fluctuating, not made permanent; <ls>U. 5. 25.</ls> {@--2@} Thrown away, unprofitable, useless; <ls>Ms. 3. 180.</ls> {@--3@} Disreputable, infamous. --ष्ठः <ab>N.</ab> of a hell. --ष्ठा Instability, ill-fame, ill-repute, dishonour. --ष्ठं Brahma (स्वधामप्रतिष्ठितं ब्रह्म).
